summary: WHILE DRIVING THE BRAKES ACTIVATED ALTHOUGH THE DRIVER DID NOT PRESS THE BRAKE PEDAL.  THE VEHICLE WAS REPAIRED AND THE PROBLEM HAS NOT RETURNED.
